And a different picture of my Dobermann this time round.
I shall return; I shall come back for you; I shall reach
out through the amorphous, swirling, Godforsaken purple 
mists of Time; I shall re-claim you...to once more have
you by my side.   What that means is I&#039;ve got some more
Bread stuff to upload.   You lot are not right.   It is a
good job I&#039;m sane.   And don&#039;t forget to pass on your
regards to Hades...otherwise he&#039;ll sulk...
